    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/9f820d9f19938f60b9862aedfa433371.avif?t=1738037605\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/cfc1204e9f2bdc1b764e5942a27f69d5.avif?t=1738037605\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>《The Outer Worlds》是一款荣获奖项的单人第一人称科幻RPG游戏，由Obsidian Entertainment和Private Divisionis联手打造。<br><br>当你探索一个太空殖民地时，你所选定的角色将决定这个玩家驱动的故事接下来将会如何展开。在这个殖民地的企业方程中，你是计划外的未知变量。<br><br><strong>主要特色</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家驱动的剧情类RPG游戏</h2>这款游戏仍延续了Obsidian的一贯做法——你在《天外世界》中的行动完全由你自己决定。你的选择不仅会影响故事的发展，而且还会改变你的角色塑造、同伴的剧情以及游戏场景。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/8cdfebe678530272b7608c64b1372d07.poster.avif?t=1738037605\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/8cdfebe678530272b7608c64b1372d07.webm?t=1738037605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/8cdfebe678530272b7608c64b1372d07.mp4?t=1738037605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你会有缺陷，但这反倒是好事</h2>《天外世界》引入的一个新特性即是缺陷概念。威震天下的盖世英雄正是由其身上的缺陷所造就的。在游玩《天外世界》时，游戏将追踪你的经历，以发现你的弱项。持续遭受机械虎攻击？那么，当你面对这种邪恶的生物时，这种机械虎恐惧症的缺陷将会让你遭受减益效果，但与此同时会即刻奖励给你额外的角色特技。这种行动选项有助于你在探索神翠的过程中丰富你的角色个性。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/3b59d2f1a16e4d89c544fcc999dd547b.poster.avif?t=1738037605\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/3b59d2f1a16e4d89c544fcc999dd547b.webm?t=1738037605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/3b59d2f1a16e4d89c544fcc999dd547b.mp4?t=1738037605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >带领你的同伴</h2>在你穿越最遥远殖民地的旅途中，你会遇到许多想要加入你团队的角色。这些同伴都拥有独特能力，且各有各的使命、动机和理想。你有责任帮助他们实现他们的目标，或者把他们变成你自己的目标。是帮助他们实现其目标，还是将他们当作实现自己目标的工具，这都取决于你。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/5275f959218510afcd4c67d37a9607f7.poster.avif?t=1738037605\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/5275f959218510afcd4c67d37a9607f7.webm?t=1738037605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/5275f959218510afcd4c67d37a9607f7.mp4?t=1738037605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索企业殖民地</h2>神翠是一个位于银河系边陲的殖民地，它隶属于一个企业董事会，并由此运营。他们控制着一切……除了那些外星怪物——它们是此殖民地两颗星球改造计划失败后的产物。寻找你的飞船，组建你的队伍，探索位于神翠殖民地的定居点、空间站和其他各种地方。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/5c7663ebdd1331a2f56ffd42adcb888b.poster.avif?t=1738037605\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/5c7663ebdd1331a2f56ffd42adcb888b.webm?t=1738037605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578650/extras/5c7663ebdd1331a2f56ffd42adcb888b.mp4?t=1738037605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
